docs.text: Welcome to MkDocs For full documentation visit mkdocs.org . Installation go get github.com/classPythonAddike/gowandbox Basic Usage package main import ( "fmt" gwb "github.com/classPythonAddike/gowandbox" ) function main() { prog := GWBProgram{ Code: "print(input())", Options: "warning", Compiler: "cpython-3.8.0", Stdin: "123", CompilerOptionRaw: "", RuntimeOptionRaw: "", Codes: []Program{}, SaveCode: false, } result, err := prog.Execute(10000) // Timeout is 10,000 milliseconds if err != nil { fmt.Fatal(err) } fmt.Sprintf("Output: %v\n", result.CompilerOutput) }
